@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram

state "Create Account" as CreateAccount
CreateAccount : entry/New user
CreateAccount : do/Provide account details
CreateAccount : exit/Account created successfully

state "Login" as Login
Login : entry/Registered user
Login : do/Enter login credentials
Login : exit/Successful login

state "Watch Videos" as WatchVideos
WatchVideos : entry/LoggedIn user
WatchVideos : do/Show available videos
WatchVideos : exit/Video played

state "Upload Video" as UploadVideo
UploadVideo : entry/LoggedIn user
UploadVideo : do/Upload new video
UploadVideo : exit/Video uploaded successfully

state "Save to Likes" as SaveLikes
SaveLikes : entry/Saving video during viewing
SaveLikes : do/Add video to likes list
SaveLikes : exit/Likes updated

state "View Liked Videos" as ViewLiked
ViewLiked : entry/User wants to view saved videos
ViewLiked : do/Show liked videos
ViewLiked : exit/Videos viewed

state "Discussion" as Discussion
Discussion : entry/User enters discussion area
Discussion : do/Participate in discussions
Discussion : exit/Discussion ended

state J0 <<choice>>
state J1 <<choice>>

[*] --> J0

J0 --> CreateAccount
J0 --> Login

CreateAccount --> J1
Login --> J1

J1 --> WatchVideos
J1 --> UploadVideo
J1 --> ViewLiked
J1 --> Discussion

WatchVideos --> SaveLikes : [Like video]
SaveLikes --> J1

UploadVideo --> J1

ViewLiked --> J1

Discussion --> J1

@enduml
